1-modify posts table to have post owner 00> owner is the current logged_in user 

2- use gates to allow the post owner to modify post

3- use policies to allow the post owner to delete the post 

4- run php artisan install:api 

5- allow only logged in users to show the post details 

6- create apis for your posts. create, update, delete , show 
